---
import DashboardLayout from "../../../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro";
---

<DashboardLayout userRole="admin">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Configuracion de la plataforma</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
        Aqui defines ajustes globales que afectan a todos los usuarios del marketplace.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 px-4 py-3 text-amber-200 text-sm">
      Esta vista ya esta organizada para admin. Falta conectar el guardado al endpoint de configuracion global.
    </div>

    <section class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-6">Ajustes generales</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <label for="platformName" class="block text-slate-400 mb-2">Nombre de la plataforma</label>
          <input
            id="platformName"
            type="text"
            value="Helium"
            class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-3"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="supportEmail" class="block text-slate-400 mb-2">Email de soporte</label>
          <input
            id="supportEmail"
            type="email"
            value="soporte@helium.com"
            class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-3"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 bg-slate-800/60 p-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium">Modo mantenimiento</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Bloquea nuevas operaciones para usuarios no admin.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
          <input id="maintenanceMode" type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5" />
          <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Activar</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-end">
        <button type="button" class="bg-purple-700 hover:bg-purple-600 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition">
          Guardar configuracion
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</DashboardLayout>
